column5: Made a trip into the Chapleau Game Preserve last week.  The Walleye fishing was amazing!!
And lots of Mid Size Pike      Report to follow  Cheers Rick
jesus,  if thats a mid size pike, I don't even think the ones I have caught would be considered small!  Great fish  **just noticed the outstreched arms...  still bigger than anything I've ever caught
Nice lunkers. Where's the rest of the pics and report?
Yea Doug  I am having a challenge in getting more than one pic in a post!! You know my computer skills!! LOL  When I get it figured out I will put up a report
Awesomse Fish. Just dying to see the rest.
You need to open a photobucket account.
Look at the head on that pike, jeez.  Looks like he needs to eat a bit more to catch of with the size of his head!!!  Nice eye
Very nice !!!! The fins on the eye are sweet lookin !!! Top predators both     Cheers !!!!!
